<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>So taboo number four:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>you can't say that your average happiness</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>has declined since having a child.</span>
